{"tid":925174,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇富比拍賣重 0.2g 月球碎石 順利以 669 萬元天價成交","createTime":"2018-12-02T15:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T17:00:05.000Z","uid":51464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcd1d3a306560008cbc33727d097d2fd479c401","tid":925174,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2220694\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2220694&d=12V0tAtH0bIVLadNMV%2BkUAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=457ea7d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2220694</a><br />\n以往曾有不少月球隕石從太空撞擊地球，從而散落在地球表面，但數量較為稀有，大約只有 1,000 顆隕石中只有 1 顆是月球隕石。最近有 3 顆月球碎石在蘇富比拍賣行中進行拍賣，這些月球碎石重量合共只有 0.2g，卻順利以 855,000 美元（折合約 669 萬港元）的價格賣出。這些月球石頭如此珍貴的原因，在於它們不是從太空撞向月球的隕石，而是太空探測器直接從月球表面取得的石頭樣本！<br />\n====================<br />\n幾粒石仔夠買兩張&quot;龍床&quot;......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59bafac1090f08f5cecac824bde115c2896066f","tid":925174,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"洗黑錢都認真啲啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc931994768f150a9a809a4dfaebb4096e544ac","tid":925174,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfFP99F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfFP99F.png&h=5271c011&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}